entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You successfully delivered Dunir's package to Toggi, and Picked up Dunir's package from the White Thranta receptionist.
entries.journal_entry_description: Bib needs you to take care of some deliveries for Dunir. It's probably best not to ask what's inside.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Dunir has asked you to drop off a package to Toggi Bok. Toggi is located just outside of Mos Eisley in a remote shipping camp. This might be a good time to break in that new speeder.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: You've delivered the package to Toggi without a hitch, and he has transmitted the delivery code to Dunir. You should be receiving word from Dunir any second now.
entries.task02_comm_message_text: I just got the payment from Toggi, good job. I just need you to do one more thing for me. I need you to go to the White Thranta Shipping offices and pick up a package for me. Here is their location.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Dunir needs one more task from you.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Dunir has asked you to pick up a package waiting for him at the White Thranta shipping office. It is inside with the receptionist.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: You have picked up the package from the receptionist. She has transmitted the pick up code to Dunir and you should be hearing from him shortly.
entries.task05_comm_message_text: I just got the pick up confirmation code from the White Thranta receptionist. Bring that to me and we can get your fee all worked out. Here's a return location for convenience.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Bring Dunir the package you picked up from the White Thranta receptionist.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: You have returned to Dunir with the package and you are waiting on your pay. Good work!
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Good Work! You have completed the Special Delivery quest.
